resources.string: xues: Wei Zheng, Ran Tao, Andres Pedroza

This application was created as part of the CST2355 course by students Wei Zheng, Ran Tao and Andres Pedroza. This app comunicates with the API ticketmaster, with this information we populate the app with valuable information about the events the user wants to know (they have toselect a city and the distance from the city).
